20G5%20is%20compatible%20with%20many%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-tv-stand%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20TV%20stands%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20by%20third-party%20manufacturers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20G5%20looks%20best%20when%20mounted%2C%20it%20still%20has%20an%20elegant%20style%20when%20placed%20on%20its%20pedestal.%20The%20display%20is%20made%20of%20premium%20materials%20and%20has%20a%20thin%20profile%20that%20measures%20just%20under%20an%20inch%20thick.%20The%20build%20and%20aesthetics%20are%20what%20you'd%20expect%20from%20such%20a%20pricey%20display%20and%20are%20a%20clear%20step%20up%20from%20the%20cheaper%20construction%20of%20more%20budget-friendly%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELG%20also%20gets%20points%20for%20including%20four%20HDMI%202.1%20ports%20to%20enable%20support%20for%20up%20to%20a%204K%2F165Hz%20signal.%20Many%20rival%20brands%2C%20including%20Sony%2C%20only%20include%20two%20HDMI%202.1%20ports%20and%20use%20HDMI%202.0%20for%20the%20remaining%20inputs.%20This%20is%20a%20great%20perk%20for%20gamers%20who%20want%20to%20connect%20multiple%20systems%20to%20the%20TV%2C%20as%20HDMI%202.1%20is%20needed%20to%20unlock%20the%20smoothest%20performance%20on%20current-gen%20consoles%20and%20high-end%20PCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222301%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person's%20hand%20holding%20an%20LG%20G5%20remote%20control%20with%20the%20TV%20blurred%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c468085e81483682cc180%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221726%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20revised%20remote%20is%20much%20more%20comfortable%20to%20hold%2C%20but%20it's%20missing%20some%20useful%20buttons.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELG%20redesigned%20its%20Magic%20Remote%20for%202025%2C%20and%20this%20new%20version%20is%20mostly%20an%20improvement.%20It%20has%20a%20thinner%2C%20more%20traditional%20shape%20instead%20of%20the%20bulky%20body%20used%20on%20past%20LG%20remotes%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20feel%20better%20in%20hand.%20Its%20main%20selection%20button%2C%20which%20doubles%20as%20a%20scroll%20wheel%2C%20also%20feels%20sturdier%2C%20making%20clicks%20more%20responsive.%20Sadly%2C%20the%20remote%20is%20not%20backlit%2C%20which%20has%20become%20standard%20on%20some%20competing%20TVs%20from%20TCL%2C%20Hisense%2C%20and%20Roku.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20past%20models%2C%20the%20Magic%20Remote%20lets%20you%20choose%20between%20navigating%20via%20standard%20button%20presses%20or%20by%20using%20motion%20controls%20(the%20%26quot%3Bmagic%26quot%3B%20part)%20to%20point%20the%20remote%20at%20the%20screen%20to%20move%20a%20virtual%20cursor.%20Unfortunately%2C%20there's%20no%20way%20to%20fully%20deactivate%20motion%20control%20if%20you%20don't%20like%20it.%20Clicking%20on%20the%20directional%20pad%20temporarily%20turns%20it%20off%2C%20but%20it%20gets%20turned%20back%20on%20if%20you%20slide%20the%20scroll%20wheel%2C%20and%20this%20is%20too%20easy%20to%20accidentally%20trigger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20remote's%20button%20layout%20has%20also%20been%20simplified%2C%20and%20I%20generally%20like%20this%20more%20minimalist%20approach.%20But%20there%20are%20two%20odd%20choices.%20First%2C%20there's%20no%20longer%20an%20input%20select%20button.%20To%20switch%20inputs%20on%20the%20TV%2C%20you%20have%20to%20hold%20down%20the%20Home%20button%20to%20pull%20up%20a%20smart%20hub%20menu%20or%20scroll%20through%20the%20homepage%20and%20find%20the%20input%20you%20like%20on%20screen.%20Second%2C%20there's%20no%20mute%20button.%20You%20can%20still%20activate%20mute%20by%20holding%20the%20remote's%20volume%20down%20button%2C%20but%20this%20means%20there's%20no%20way%20to%20rapidly%20lower%20the%20volume%20instead%20of%20fully%20muting%20it.%20These%20are%20small%20complaints%2C%20but%20they%20just%20strike%20me%20as%20strange%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22932677bc-b0fa-46f0-a7f7-000e7dc34011%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Performance%5C%22%3EThe%20G5%20delivers%20a%20new%20benchmark%20for%20premium%20image%20quality%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221580%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20LG%20G5%20TV%20on%20a%20media%20console%20displaying%20an%20image%20of%20a%20river.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c4995f748d8c055f45af1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221185%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20G5%20is%20the%20brightest%20OLED%20TV%20on%20the%20market.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20G5%20is%20the%20first%20consumer%20TV%20to%20use%20LG's%20new%20four-stack%20OLED%20panel%20design.%20This%20type%20of%20screen%20has%20key%20benefits%20over%20the%20standard%20WOLED%20panel%20used%20on%20LG's%20cheaper%20C%20and%20B%20series%20TVs.%20A%20four-stack%20design%20optimizes%20how%20an%20OLED%20produces%20color%20and%20light%2C%20allowing%20for%20higher%20brightness%20and%20a%20wider%20color%20gamut%20%E2%80%94%20all%20while%20maintaining%20the%20pixel-level%20contrast%2C%20deep%20black%20levels%2C%20and%20wide%20viewing%20angles%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-oled-tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20OLED%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20known%20for.%20You%20can%20learn%20more%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fqled-vs-oled%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EQLED%20vs.%20OLED%20comparison%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20are%20spectacular%2C%20and%20the%20TV%20offers%20a%20big%20leap%20in%20brightness%20over%20last%20year's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Flg-g4-oled-4k-tv-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EG4%20model%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20G5%20is%20now%20the%20brightest%20OLED%20TV%20available%2C%20dethroning%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsamsung-s95f-oled-4k-tv-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESamsung%20S95F%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Using%20the%20TV's%20Filmmaker%20mode%20with%20a%2010%25%20HDR%20test%20pattern%20(a%20white%20box%20that%20takes%20up%2010%25%20of%20the%20screen%20against%20a%20black%20background)%2C%20I%20measured%20a%20peak%20brightness%20of%202%2C410%20nits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20nearly%201%2C000%20nits%20more%20than%20last%20year's%20G4%2C%20which%20is%20a%20substantial%20bump.%20It's%20also%20about%20240%20nits%20more%20than%20the%20S95F%2C%20which%20is%20a%20more%20subtle%20but%20still%20noteworthy%20jump.%20While%20such%20high%20brightness%20is%20impressive%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20it's%20only%20beneficial%20in%20certain%20circumstances.%20For%20example%2C%20high%20brightness%20gives%20you%20more%20headroom%20to%20pump%20up%20luminance%20to%20help%20overcome%20glare%20in%20rooms%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20ambient%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20allows%20the%20G5%20to%20produce%20more%20impactful%20and%20accurate%20high%20dynamic%20range%20(HDR)%20images%20with%20highlights%20(like%20explosions)%20that%20pop%20from%20the%20screen.%20But%20the%20G5's%20full%20brightness%20capabilities%20only%20get%20unleashed%20when%20watching%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%20mastered%20for%20above%201%2C000%20nits.%20You%20can%20learn%20more%20about%20HDR%20mastering%20and%20how%20it%20relates%20to%20content%20and%20TVs%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-hdr-tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHDR%20guide%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222212%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20view%20of%20an%20LG%20G5%20TV%20displaying%20an%20image%20of%20a%20lion%20in%20front%20of%20a%20pack%20of%20elephants.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c5d4785e81483682cc588%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221659%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUnlike%20most%20competing%20QLED%20TVs%2C%20the%20G5's%20picture%20doesn't%20fade%20or%20get%20washed%20out%20when%20viewed%20from%20an%20angle.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERaw%20brightness%20is%20only%20a%20part%20of%20what%20makes%20the%20G5's%20image%20quality%20so%20noteworthy.%20What%20makes%20this%20TV%20shine%20is%20how%20it's%20able%20to%20precisely%20harness%20its%20brightness%20and%20combine%20it%20with%20pixel-level%20contrast%20control%2C%20inky%20black%20levels%2C%20and%20rich%20colors.%20I%20watched%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%20across%20several%20weeks%20with%20the%20G5%2C%20and%20I've%20never%20seen%20a%20consumer%20TV%20that%20matches%20its%20picture%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20its%20benefits%20over%20other%20high-end%20sets%20are%20subtle%2C%20and%20it%20has%20some%20flaws%20that%20a%20few%20rivals%20handle%20better%2C%20but%20overall%2C%20the%20G5%20rises%20above%20the%20competition.%20Fiery%20explosions%20in%20high-brightness%20HDR%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BMad%20Max%3A%20Fury%20Road%26quot%3B%20radiate%20from%20the%20screen%20with%20rich%20saturation%2C%20while%20deep%20shadows%20in%20the%20opening%20sequence%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Matrix%26quot%3B%20remain%20perfectly%20dark%20without%20any%20halos%20around%20lighter%20elements%20of%20the%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETricky%20sequences%20in%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3B1917%26quot%3B%20and%20shows%20like%20%26quot%3BChilling%20Adventures%20of%20Sabrina%26quot%3B%20that%20trip%20up%20the%20local%20dimming%20backlights%20on%20many%20QLED%20TVs%20I've%20tested%20are%20displayed%20with%20perfect%2C%20uniform%20contrast.%20And%20image%20quality%20barely%20shifts%20if%20you're%20off%20to%20the%20side%20of%20the%20screen%2C%20so%20everyone%20gets%20a%20good%20viewing%20experience%20no%20matter%20where%20they%20sit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELG's%20picture%20processing%20continues%20to%20improve%20year%20after%20year%2C%20and%20the%20G5%20is%20able%20to%20hold%20its%20own%20against%20high-end%20Sony%20TVs.%20Lower-quality%20content%20like%20compressed%20HD%20YouTube%20streams%20and%20cable%20TV%20upscale%20nicely%20on%20the%20G5.%20To%20be%20clear%2C%20they%20still%20don't%20look%20as%20good%20as%20native%204K%20sources%2C%20but%20the%20TV%20does%20a%20good%20job%20of%20minimizing%20imperfections%20without%20introducing%20an%20unnatural%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221669%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20view%20of%20an%20LG%20G5%20TV%20on%20a%20media%20console%20displaying%20an%20image%20of%20a%20giraffe%20walking%20in%20front%20of%20the%20setting%20sun.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c5ec2f748d8c055f45eda%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221252%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20G5's%20deep%20black%20levels%20and%20high%20contrast%20enable%20incredible%20HDR%20images%20with%20rich%20colors%20and%20inky%20shadows.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20phenomenal%20as%20the%20G5%20is%2C%20the%20TV's%20image%20quality%20isn't%20flawless.%20When%20it%20first%20hit%20stores%2C%20the%20G5%20had%20issues%20with%20color%20banding%2C%20also%20called%20posterization%20or%20false%20contouring.%20This%20caused%20some%20gradations%20of%20colors%20and%20dark%20shades%20to%20look%20blocky%20rather%20than%20smooth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20problem%20initially%20appeared%20in%20some%20Dolby%20Vision%20and%20HDR10%20content%2C%20but%20during%20my%20testing%2C%20LG%20released%20a%20firmware%20update%20that%20corrected%20Dolby%20Vision%20playback.%20However%2C%20some%20banding%20still%20popped%20up%20in%20isolated%20scenes%20when%20watching%20a%20small%20selection%20of%20HDR10%20videos.%20But%20throughout%20my%20weeks%20with%20the%20TV%2C%20this%20flaw%20was%20very%20subtle%20and%20only%20appeared%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20movies%20I%20sampled%20out%20of%20more%20than%20a%20dozen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20my%20evaluation%20period%20ended%2C%20LG%20released%20another%20firmware%20update%20in%20June.%20This%20latest%20version%20reportedly%20corrects%20those%20lingering%20problems%20with%20HDR10%20so%20long%20as%20you%20use%20the%20TV's%20Filmmaker%20preset.%20With%20all%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20I%20don't%20consider%20this%20to%20be%20a%20major%20drawback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20small%20imperfection%20I%20encountered%20involved%20some%20slight%20over-brightening%20in%20near-black%20content%2C%20which%20caused%20dark%20shades%20to%20faintly%20glow.%20I%20noticed%20this%20a%20bit%20when%20watching%20some%20dim%20sequences%20in%20the%20Amazon%20Prime%20series%20%26quot%3BThe%20Wheel%20of%20Time%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20was%20never%20too%20distracting.%20This%20issue%20is%20common%20on%20OLED%20displays%20like%20this%2C%20and%20the%20G5%20performs%20about%20on%20par%20with%20what's%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20it's%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20while%20the%20G5%20rises%20above%20competing%20flagship%20OLEDs%20in%20nearly%20every%20way%2C%20there%20is%20one%20area%20where%20top%20models%20from%20Samsung%20and%20Sony%20still%20have%20a%20slight%20edge%3A%20color%20volume.%20High-end%20OLEDs%20from%20those%20brands%20use%20quantum%20dots%2C%20which%20is%20a%20feature%20the%20G5%20is%20missing.%20This%20allows%20those%20TVs%20to%20maintain%20high%20saturation%20a%20bit%20better%20when%20displaying%20especially%20bright%20colors.%20The%20G5%20improves%20upon%20the%20G4%20in%20this%20area%2C%20but%20it%20still%20can't%20quite%20match%20OLEDs%20that%20have%20quantum%20dots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222af179d3-4c5e-4261-8c16-f6164aeb237a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Gaming%20features%5C%22%3EGamers%20get%20cool%20features%20like%20a%20165Hz%20refresh%20rate%20and%20support%20for%20Xbox%20streaming%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222384%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20LG%20G5%204K%20HDR%20TV%20on%20a%20media%20console%20with%20Spider-Man%20on%20PS5%20playing%20on%20the%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c475c85e81483682cc1a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221788%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20G5%20has%20excellent%20gaming%20performance%20with%20a%20handy%20Game%20Optimizer%20menu.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20G5%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20advanced%20gaming%20TVs%20there%20is.%20It%20supports%20ALLM%20(auto%20low%20latency%20mode)%2C%20VRR%20(variable%20refresh%20rate)%2C%20and%20a%20dedicated%20Game%20Optimizer%20menu%20that%20lets%20you%20easily%20adjust%20settings.%20The%20G5%20sets%20itself%20apart%20from%20most%20competing%20TVs%20with%20its%20support%20for%20up%20to%20a%20165Hz%20refresh%20rate.%20Most%20high-end%20TVs%20max%20out%20at%20144Hz.%20This%20is%20only%20useful%20for%20PC%20gamers%20with%20high-end%20hardware%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20a%20cool%20perk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELG%20is%20also%20one%20of%20two%20brands%20(Samsung%20is%20the%20other)%20that%20supports%20the%20Xbox%20app%20directly%20through%20the%20TV's%20interface.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fxbox-game-pass%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGame%20Pass%3C%2Fa%3E%20membership%2C%20this%20app%20lets%20you%20stream%20Xbox%20games%20so%20you%20can%20play%20them%20without%20needing%20a%20console.%20The%20quality%20isn't%20as%20good%20as%20playing%20a%20game%20directly%20through%20a%20system%2C%20and%20playability%20is%20heavily%20reliant%20on%20the%20stability%20of%20your%20internet%20connection%2C%20but%20it%20works%20well%20enough%20for%20casual%20gaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20tested%20the%20G5%20with%20a%20PS5%20using%20a%204K%2F120Hz%20connection%2C%20and%20it%20delivered%20excellent%20image%20quality%20and%20smooth%20motion.%20I%20didn't%20see%20any%20flicker%20or%20ghosting%20with%20VRR%20active%2C%20which%20is%20something%20I've%20seen%20on%20some%20QLED%20TVs.%20Some%20flicker%20did%20show%20up%20when%20I%20pulled%20up%20the%20TV's%20settings%20menu%20while%20playing%20games%2C%20but%20this%20went%20away%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20closed%20the%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I've%20seen%20some%20user%20reports%20of%20banding%20in%20certain%20games%20when%20using%20the%20TV's%20HDR%20Game%20mode%2C%20even%20after%20the%20latest%20firmware%20update%20released%20in%20June.%20But%20outside%20some%20subtle%20bands%20in%20the%20sky%20when%20playing%20%26quot%3BCyberpunk%202077%26quot%3B%20and%20some%20slight%20contouring%20in%20menus%2C%20I%20didn't%20encounter%20any%20egregious%20banding%20when%20playing%20various%20HDR%20titles%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BThe%20Last%20of%20Us%20Part%201%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BSpider-Man%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BNo%20Man's%20Sky%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BDragon's%20Dogma%202%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BBaldur's%20Gate%203.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ece31886-a674-47ef-94c7-b113a92932d0%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Smart%20TV%20interface%5C%22%3ELG's%20webOS%20adds%20some%20new%20AI%20features%2C%20but%20they're%20mostly%20unnecessary%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20LG%20G5%20TV%20displaying%20the%20webOS%20homepage.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c492285e81483682cc204%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222437%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELG's%20webOS%20interface%20is%20decent%2C%20but%20we%20prefer%20platforms%20like%20Google%20TV%20and%20Roku.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20all%20LG%20TVs%2C%20the%20G5%20uses%20the%20webOS%20smart%20TV%20system.%20The%20platform%20is%20easy%20to%20set%20up%2C%20as%20LG%20guides%20you%20through%20some%20basic%20housekeeping%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20interface%20has%20access%20to%20all%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fbest-streaming-services%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20streaming%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%20it's%20missing%20a%20few%20niche%20apps%20that%20some%20other%20platforms%20support%2C%20like%20the%20Criterion%20Channel.%20General%20navigation%20is%20smooth%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20encounter%20any%20major%20lag%20when%20moving%20through%20services.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20interface's%20design%20could%20annoy%20some%20users.%20By%20default%2C%20webOS%20displays%20a%20banner%20ad%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20homepage%2C%20and%20the%20screen%20prominently%20features%20a%20row%20for%20shopping%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20deactivate%20the%20banner%20ad%20if%20you%20navigate%20through%20some%20buried%20menu%20options%2C%20but%20this%20leaves%20that%20space%20unutilized.%20You%20can%20also%20turn%20off%20the%20shopping%20recommendations%2C%20but%20this%20deactivates%20all%20of%20the%20platform's%20content%20suggestions%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20barebones%20interface.%20It's%20great%20that%20LG%20offers%20the%20option%20to%20fully%20deactivate%20the%20ads%2C%20but%20I%20wish%20there%20was%20a%20better%20balance%20to%20begin%20with%2C%20so%20it%20could%20display%20content%20recommendations%20while%20demphasizing%20some%20of%20the%20sponsored%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%202025%2C%20LG%20is%20touting%20a%20lot%20of%20new%20AI%20features%2C%20but%20most%20of%20these%20functions%20are%20just%20improved%20iterations%20of%20features%20that%20have%20already%20been%20available%20on%20past-generation%20TVs.%20For%20instance%2C%20there%20are%20AI%20picture%20modes%20that%20are%20meant%20to%20enhance%20the%20image%2C%20especially%20with%20lower-quality%20content%2C%20but%20the%20adjustments%20these%20modes%20make%20are%20unnecessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20also%20brought%20back%20its%20AI%20Picture%20Wizard%20and%20added%20a%20new%20AI%20Audio%20Wizard.%20These%20features%20present%20you%20with%20various%20sample%20images%20and%20audio%20clips.%20Based%20on%20which%20ones%20you%20select%2C%20the%20wizard%20learns%20what%20kind%20of%20picture%20and%20sound%20settings%20you%20like%20the%20most%2C%20and%20then%20creates%20custom%20modes%20for%20you.%20Again%2C%20I%20highly%20recommend%20just%20using%20the%20TV's%20Filmmaker%20mode%20and%20Standard%20audio%20mode%20to%20get%20the%20most%20accurate%20playback%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20unhappy%20with%20how%20the%20G5%20looks%20or%20sounds%2C%20this%20is%20worth%20playing%20around%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221384%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20LG%20G5%20TV%20displaying%20the%20AI%20concierge%20menu.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c485bf748d8c055f45ab6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221038%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELG's%20AI%20concierge%20offers%20content%20recommendations%2C%20but%20they%20didn't%20seem%20to%20relate%20much%20to%20my%20viewing%20habits.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELG's%20remote%20also%20emphasizes%20AI%20more%20this%20year%2C%20as%20the%20microphone%20button%20has%20been%20rebranded%20as%20the%20AI%20button.%20Pressing%20it%20pulls%20up%20LG's%20AI%20concierge.%20This%20is%20supposed%20to%20present%20smart%20content%20recommendations%20based%20on%20your%20viewing%20habits%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20find%20them%20to%20be%20all%20that%20useful.%20Holding%20down%20the%20AI%20button%20allows%20you%20to%20search%20with%20your%20voice%20or%20speak%20commands%20to%20control%20the%20TV.%20The%20G5%20also%20supports%20hands-free%20voice%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20sure%20what%20the%20issue%20was%2C%20but%20during%20my%20first%20week%20or%20so%20with%20the%20TV%2C%20I%20ran%20into%20a%20lot%20of%20server%20errors%20and%20%26quot%3Bvoice%20not%20recognized%26quot%3B%20messages%20when%20using%20the%20G5's%20voice%20search.%20Over%20time%2C%20these%20glitches%20stopped%20popping%20up%2C%20and%20voice%20search%20worked%20consistently.%20That%20said%2C%20I%20found%20the%20TV's%20voice%20recognition%20to%20be%20less%20accurate%20and%20slower%20than%20some%20competing%20systems%2C%20like%20Roku%20and%20Google%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20plus%20side%2C%20the%20G5%20does%20have%20a%20new%20voice%20feature%20that's%20actually%20pretty%20cool.%20It's%20called%20AI%20voice%20recognition%2C%20and%20it%20automatically%20switches%20user%20profiles%20based%20on%20who%20speaks%20to%20the%20TV.%20So%2C%20if%20your%20spouse%20was%20using%20the%20set%20and%20you%20both%20have%20different%20profiles%2C%20once%20you%20speak%20to%20the%20TV%2C%20it%20will%20switch%20to%20your%20personalized%20home%20screen%20with%20your%20preferences%20and%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c23df8c8-1630-427c-a047-8e8fe0e24b08%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20it%3F%5C%22%3EShould%20you%20buy%20the%20LG%20G5%20TV%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222205%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Angled%20view%20of%20an%20LG%20G5%20OLED%20TV%20on%20a%20media%20console%20displaying%20a%20close-up%20image%20of%20a%20lion's%20face.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c5f5e3d5881a51c1c170b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221654%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20G5%20is%20the%20ideal%20TV%20for%20home%20theater%20fans%20focused%20on%20picture%20quality.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFew%20TVs%20have%20left%20me%20as%20utterly%20impressed%20as%20the%20LG%20G5.%20Some%20competing%20high-end%20sets%20from%20Sony%20and%20Samsung%20offer%20better%20performance%20in%20certain%20aspects%2C%20but%20when%20looking%20at%20picture%20quality%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20the%20G5%20is%20the%20best%20premium%20display%20I've%20seen.%20Panasonic%20is%20set%20to%20release%20a%20