nted%20to%20getting%20paid%20quickly%20as%20one%20of%20the%20top%20reasons%20they%20choose%20to%20drive%20for%20the%20app%2C%20with%20about%20seven%20in%2010%20%26quot%3BDashers%26quot%3B%20expecting%20to%20use%20their%20dashing%20income%20within%20the%20week%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20one%20in%20four%20DoorDash%20drivers%20expect%20to%20use%20their%20pay%20within%20days%2C%20per%20the%20DoorDash%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Lyft%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20roughly%2030%25%20of%20payouts%20through%20the%20app%20are%20deposited%20through%20its%20express%20payment%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20other%20gig%20driving%20apps%2C%20including%20Uber%20and%20Instacart%2C%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWyatt%20Taylor%2C%20a%2019-year-old%20DoorDash%20driver%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20relies%20on%20the%20app's%20partnership%20with%20Crimson%20to%20get%20his%20pay%20delivered%20directly%20to%20a%20personal%20banking%20account%20immediately%2C%20free%20of%20charge%2C%20after%20every%20trip%20he%20makes%20for%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20need%20to%20make%20something%20happen%2C%20like%20if%20you're%20needing%20to%20fill%20up%20your%20gas%20tank%2C%20then%20you're%20not%20having%20to%20wait%20till%20Monday%2C%26quot%3B%20Taylor%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20just%20do%20a%20DoorDash%2C%20and%20then%20after%20you're%20done%2C%20you%20can%20just%20go%20and%20take%20your%20car%20to%20the%20gas%20station.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20quick%20turnaround%20is%20increasingly%20important%20to%20drivers%20trying%20to%20maintain%20a%20longer%20financial%20runway%2C%20Everee%20found.%20The%20Everee%20survey%20found%2C%20in%20general%2C%2065%25%20of%20respondents%20had%20taken%20a%20payday%20loan%20or%20cash%20advance%20because%20payouts%20lagged%2C%20and%2061%25%20delayed%20paying%20a%20bill%20or%20making%20an%20essential%20purchase%20while%20waiting%20for%20their%20earnings%20to%20hit%20their%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStephanie%20Riggs%2C%20a%2054-year-old%20driver%20who%20uses%20the%20catering%20delivery%20app%2C%20Dlivrd%2C%20told%20BI%20that%2C%20while%20she%20generally%20prefers%20to%20stack%20her%20payments%20for%20weekly%20cashouts%2C%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20she%20prefers%20to%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-uber-driver-thrill-of-claiming-rides-can-take-over-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egig%20driving%3C%2Fa%3E%20her%20full-time%20job%20is%20the%20freedom%20in%20both%20working%20hours%20and%20payment%20options%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0so%20%26quot%3Bif%20I%20was%20ever%20in%20a%20situation%20where%20there%20was%20an%20emergency%2C%20those%20funds%20are%20available%20and%20flexible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f6519983-ba0c-4281-ba81-e902ff040ba1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFaster%20pay%20is%20gaining%20traction%20across%20industries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20for%20flexible%20payment%20options%20is%20expanding%20beyond%20traditional%20gig%20work%2C%20as%20well.%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported%20Gen%20Z%20is%20bringing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-gig-economy-mindset-corporate-america-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egig%20work%20mentality%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20corporate%20America%2C%20and%20some%20corporations%20are%20taking%20notice%20of%20the%20preference%20for%20more%20customizable%20ways%20to%20access%20their%20paycheck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETate%20Hackert%2C%20cofounder%20and%20Chief%20Strategy%20Officer%20of%20ZayZoon%2C%20a%20software%20company%20that%20provides%20employees%20with%20access%20to%20their%20earned%20wages%20before%20payday%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20many%20franchised%20McDonald's%20locations%20use%20his%20company's%20software%2C%20as%20well%20as%20brick-and-mortar%20businesses%20like%20coffee%20shops%20and%20