ed%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20first%20worked%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-fabulous-life-of-anna-wintour-2016-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnna%20Wintour%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20New%20York%20Magazine%2C%20where%20I%20was%20an%20editorial%20assistant%20in%20the%20early%2080s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20became%20Vogue's%20creative%20director%20in%201983%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20go%20with%20her%20to%20be%20a%20fly%20on%20the%20wall%20of%20her%20process.%20Though%20she%20wasn't%20warm%20and%20fuzzy%2C%20she%20was%20an%20incredible%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20continued%20to%20work%20with%20Anna%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvogue-new-york-city-fashion-week-street-fair-anniversary-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVogue%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20two%20separate%20stints%2C%20and%20at%20House%20%26amp%3B%20Garden%2C%20another%20Cond%C3%A9%20Nast%20title%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20with%20Anna%2C%20I%20got%20to%20know%20how%20soft%20she%20is%20on%20the%20inside.%20She's%20done%20amazing%20things%20for%20people%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20including%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232326ad7-6142-4c49-9bd5-2a6dedad30c8%5C%22%3EI%20followed%20in%20Anna%20Wintour's%20footsteps%20for%20a%20chunk%20of%20my%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnna%20was%20friends%20with%20my%20friend%20before%20I%20worked%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%20said%20Anna%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20new%20assistant%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-magazine-big-success-pop-up-newsletters-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20should%20apply.%20But%20I%20didn't%20get%20the%20job.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20that%20assistant%20quit%2C%20so%20Anna%20called%20my%20office%20and%20asked%20if%20I%20was%20interested.%20I%20said%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnna%20is%20sup