of%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20dress%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685ecffd85e81483682cf011%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELaurie%20Schechter%2C%20pictured%20in%202023.%3Cp%3EPatrick%20McMullan%2FPMC%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20first%20things%20she%20did%20at%20Vogue%20was%20talk%20to%20all%20the%20staff.%20She%20gave%20people%20an%20opportunity%20to%20see%20what%20she%20was%20all%20about.%20Some%20people%20decided%20not%20to%20stay%20on%2C%20but%20others%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286b1450f-0b35-44cd-b0c3-b37e9f6794ad%5C%22%3EAnna%20may%20be%20prickly%20on%20the%20outside%2C%20but%20she's%20soft%20on%20the%20inside%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnna%20was%20very%20cut-and-dried.%20Once%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20do%20a%20page%20on%20a%20theme%20that%20wasn't%20Anna's%20cup%20of%20tea.%20She%20gave%20me%20permission%20to%20go%20ahead%2C%20so%20I%20did%20a%20shoot%20and%20brought%20it%20back%20to%20her.%20When%20we%20laid%20out%20the%20story%2C%20she%20hated%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20argued%20my%20case%2C%20and%20she%20listened%2C%20but%20she%20eventually%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BLaurie%2C%20drop%20it.%26quot%3B%20That's%20very%20much%20Anna.%20She%20gave%20me%20the%20chance%20to%20change%20her%20mind%2C%20but%20if%20something%20didn't%20work%20for%20her%2C%20that%20was%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20called%20her%20%26quot%3Bice%20queen%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanna-wintour-on-leadership-and-management-2016-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enuclear%20Wintour%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20I%20actually%20think%20she%20has%20a%20maternal%20side%20she%20doesn't%20show%20to%20everyone.%20A%20prickly%20pear%20is%20spiky%20on%20the%20outside%2C%20but%20soft%20and%20sweet%20on%20the%20inside%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20like%20Anna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20seen%20her%20do%