0New%20Cantt.%20The%20vibrant%20demonstration%2C%20with%20children%20holding%20signs%20reading%20%E2%80%9CSave%20Our%20Trees%E2%80%9D%20and%20elders%20chanting%20for%20sustainability%2C%20forced%20authorities%20to%20halt%20the%20project%2C%20saving%20all%20250%20trees.%20CFGD%E2%80%99s%20Chipko%202.0%20campaign%20has%20protected%20trees%20in%20Khalanga%E2%80%99s%20forests%2C%20while%20their%20symbolic%20%E2%80%9Ctree%20funeral%E2%80%9D%20for%20felled%20trees%20gives%20%3Cem%3Eshraddhanjali%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20those%20who%20work%20for%20us%20their%20entire%20lives%20and%20leave%20silently%20without%20saying%20much%E2%80%94the%20trees.%20This%20silent%20movement%20drew%20many%20to%20mourn%20the%20loss%20of%20Dehradun%E2%80%99s%20green%20heritage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-6_11zon-1751011492.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20protest%20during%20a%20heatwave%20saved%20250%20trees%20from%20being%20cut%20in%20New%20Cantt%20thanks%20to%20CFGD%20and%203%2C000%20citizens.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-6_11zon-1751011492.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-6_11zon-1751011492-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-6_11zon-1751011492-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-6_11zon-1751011492-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-6_11zon-1751011492-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-456927%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20protest%20during%20a%20heatwave%