un%20is%20relatively%20pest-resistant%2C%20but%20aphids%20or%20fruit%20flies%20can%20occasionally%20attack.%20Use%20neem%20oil%20spray%20or%20homemade%20garlic-chilli%20spray%20once%20a%20month%20to%20keep%20pests%20at%20bay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E10.%20Jamun%20needs%20a%20lot%20of%20patience%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamun%20trees%20take%20their%20time.%20Depending%20on%20whether%20you%E2%80%99ve%20planted%20from%20seed%20or%20a%20grafted%20sapling%2C%20the%20tree%20may%20start%20fruiting%20in%20four%20to%20eight%20years.%20But%20once%20it%20starts%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20have%20a%20summer%20bounty%20of%20sweet%2C%20astringent%20fruits%20packed%20with%20health%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKey%20points%20to%20remember%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F414458%2Flesser-known-indian-summer-fruits-benefits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJamun%20loves%20the%20sun%20and%20thrives%20in%20full%20sunlight.%3C%2Fa%3E%20To%20ensure%20healthy%20growth%20and%20fruiting%2C%20make%20sure%20your%20plant%20gets%20at%20least%20six%20hours%20of%20direct%20sunlight%20every%20day.%20Shady%20spots%20or%20indoor%20corners%20just%20won%E2%80%99t%20do%20%E2%80%94%20it%20needs%20light%20to%20photosynthesize%20efficiently%20and%20produce%20quality%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Soil%20should%20drain%20well%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamun%20trees%20do%20not%20appreciate%20wet%20feet!%20While%20they%20can%20adapt%20to%20different%20soil%20types%2C%20loamy%20or%20sandy-loam%20soil%20with%20good%20drainage%20is%20ideal.%20Waterlogged%20soil%20can%20lead%20to%20root%20rot%20and%20fungal%20infections.%20Mix%20in%20some%20sand%20or%20cocopeat%20if%20your%20garden%20soil%20tends%20to%20retain%20too%20much%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Use%20grafted%20saplings%20for%20faster%20results%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20Jamun%20from%20seed%20is%20possible%20but%20requires%20immense%20patience%2C%20as%20it%20can%20take%20eight%20to%2010%20years%20to%20fruit.%20Grafted%20saplings%2C%20however%2C%20are%20clones%20of%20mature%20trees%20and%20typically%20start%20bearing%20fruit%20in%20just%20four%20to%20five%20years.%20You%E2%80%99ll%20also%20have%20a%20better%20idea%20of%20fruit%20quality%20and%20tree%20size%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Water%20less%2C%20not%20more%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamun%20is%20a%20hardy%2C%20drought-tolerant%20tree.%20During%20the%20monsoon%2C%20natural%20rainfall%20is%20usually%20sufficient.%20Only%20water%20if%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20dry%20spell%20or%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20growing%20it%20in%20a%20container.%20Let%20the%20topsoil%20dry%20slightly%20before%20watering%20again.%20Overwatering%2C%20especially%20in%20pots%2C%20can%20stunt%20growth%20or%20damage%20the%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Fruits%20stain%2C%20but%20soothe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20Jamun%20stains%20your%20tongue%20and%20hands%20a%20deep%20purple%E2%80%94but%20it%E2%80%99s%20worth%20it.%20The%20fruit%20is%20low%20in%20calories%20but%20high%20in%20antioxidants%2C%20Vitamin%20C%2C%20and%20iron.%20It%20helps%20regulate%20blood%20sugar%20levels%2C%20aids%20digestion%2C%20improves%20immunity%2C%20and%20even%20benefits%20skin%20health.%20It%E2%80%99s%20your%20very%20own%20medicinal%20fruit%20basket!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Grow%20health%2C%20not%20just%20a%20tree%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlanting%20a%20Jamun%20tree%20is%20an%20act%20of%20slow%2C%20joyful%20patience.%20It%20won%E2%80%99t%20give%20instant%20gratification%2C%20but%20in%20a%20few%20years%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20have%20a%20personal%20source%20of%20antioxidants%2C%20immunity%2C%20and%20nostalgia%20(who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20remember%20purple%20tongues%20in%20school%3F).%20So%20this%20monsoon%2C%20instead%20of%20just%20watching%20the%20rain%2C%20plant%20a%20little%20legacy.%20One%20fruit%2C%20one%20tree%2C%20one%20immune-boosting%20bite%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Vidya%20Gowri%20Venkatesh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750851000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-06-25T154635.803-1750846608.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D455484%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Forget%20the%20farm%20%E2%80%94%20Jamun%20trees%20can%20thrive%20in%20your%20backyard%20or%20even%20on%20your%20balcony.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20to%20grow%20this%20immunity-boosting%20fruit%20at%20home%20this%20monsoon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F455484%2Fhow-to-grow-jamun-in-monsoon%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20the%20Monsoon%20Is%20the%20Best%20Time%20to%20Start%20Growing%20Your%20Own%20Kitchen%20Garden%20at%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMonsoon%20season%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F441584%2Fhow-to-compost-during-monsoon-tips-challenges-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enature%E2%80%99s%20way%20of%20replenishing%20the%20earth%20with%20much-needed%20water%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20cooling%20down%20the%20relentless%20summer%20heat.%20The%20soft%20drizzle%2C%20the%20earthy%20scent%20of%20wet%20soil%2C%20and%20the%20greenery%20make%20it%20feel%20like%20the%20world%20is%20breathing%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImagine%20stepping%20out%20barefoot%20onto%